## id: infoblox-nios-panel
## name: Infoblox NIOS Login Panel - Detect
## author: hack007x
## severity: info
## tags: panel,infoblox,nios,login,detect,discovery
## description: Infoblox NIOS login panel was detected.
## affects: nios
## reference: https://www.infoblox.com/glossary/network-identity-operating-system-nios/
